graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|container orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.19+<br/>Required]
    KubeRay -->|distributed computing| Ray[Ray 2.0+<br/>Required<br/>Container Images]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|external access| IngressController[Ingress Controller<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|external access| OpenShiftRoutes[OpenShift Routes<br/>Optional - OpenShift only]
    KubeRay -.->|webhook TLS certs| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Optional]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano[Volcano / Yunikorn<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KubeRay -->|inference runtime| ModelMesh[Model Mesh<br/>Ray Serve Integration]
    KubeRay -->|job submission| NotebookController[Notebook Controller<br/>Jupyter → Ray Client]
    KubeRay -.->|monitoring UI| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Ray Cluster Status]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    KubeRay -->|pull images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, registry.access.redhat.com]
    KubeRay -->|data storage| S3[S3 / Object Storage<br/>Training Data & Models]
    KubeRay -.->|HA GCS backend| ExternalRedis[External Redis<br/>Optional]

    %% Kubernetes API Groups
    subgraph K8sAPIs["Kubernetes API Dependencies"]
        CoreAPI[Core API<br/>pods, services, endpoints, events]
        BatchAPI[Batch API<br/>jobs]
        RBACAPI[RBAC API<br/>roles, rolebindings]
        NetworkingAPI[Networking API<br/>ingresses]
        CoordinationAPI[Coordination API<br/>leases - leader election]
        RayAPI[ray.io API Group<br/>rayclusters, rayjobs, rayservices]
    end

    K8s --> CoreAPI
    K8s --> BatchAPI
    K8s --> RBACAPI
    K8s --> NetworkingAPI
    K8s --> CoordinationAPI
    K8s --> RayAPI

    %% Integration Points
    subgraph IntegrationPoints["Integration Points"]
        K8sAPIServer[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+]
        PrometheusIntegration[Prometheus<br/>HTTP/8080 Metrics Scraping]
        IngressIntegration[Ingress Controller<br/>HTTP Proxy 8265/10001]
        ObjectStorageIntegration[Object Storage<br/>S3 API 443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    KubeRay -->|watch/reconcile| K8sAPIServer
    KubeRay -->|exposes metrics| PrometheusIntegration
    KubeRay -->|creates ingress| IngressIntegration
    KubeRay -->|workloads access| ObjectStorageIntegration

    %% Styling
    style KubeRay fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    style K8s fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Ray fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    style Prometheus fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style IngressController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style OpenShiftRoutes fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CertManager fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Volcano fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ExternalRedis fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    style ModelMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% External Services
    style ContainerRegistry fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Kubernetes APIs
    style CoreAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666
    style BatchAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666
    style RBACAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666
    style NetworkingAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666
    style CoordinationAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#666
    style RayAPI fill:#cfe2f3,stroke:#3d85c6,stroke-width:2px
